.1</span> 标题：城墙、外郭、城垛（city wall, rampart, battlement）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：גְּבוּל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：gvul)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:12\">ISA 54:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：גָּדֵר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：gader)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:11\">MIC 7:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：חֵיל, חַיִל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：chel, chayil, cheylah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam20:15\">2SA 20:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:23\">1KI 21:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps48:14\">PSA 48:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps122:7\">PSA 122:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:1\">ISA 26:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:8\">LAM 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:8\">NAM 3:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：חוֹמָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：chomah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:22\">EXO 14:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:29\">EXO 14:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:29\">LEV 25:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:30\">LEV 25:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:31\">LEV 25:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:5\">DEU 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:52\">DEU 28:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:5\">JOS 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:20\">JOS 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam31:10\">1SA 31:10</a>, <a href=\"htt